OL,3,CJail warning for teen who threw bottle
OL,4,Cand stole policeman's hat during riots
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy has been warned he
OL,7,Fmay be jailed after admitting throwing
OL,8,Fa glass bottle and stealing a
OL,9,Fpoliceman's hat.
OL,11,FThe youngster, from the Bolton area,
OL,12,Fappeared at Manchester Youth Court,
OL,13,Faccompanied by his parents, where he
OL,14,Fadmitted the charge of violent
OL,15,Fdisorder and the theft of the #30 hat
OL,16,Fbelonging to Greater Manchester Police.
