OL,3,CJail warning for teen who threw bottle
OL,4,Cand stole policeman's hat during riots
OL,6,FThe court heard he who took part in
OL,7,F"large scale disorder" in Bolton town
OL,8,Fcentre on 4 August, as trouble hit
OL,9,Ftowns and cities across the UK
OL,10,Ffollowing the stabbing to death of
OL,11,Fthree children in Southport.
OL,13,FThe boy, who cannot be identified
OL,14,Fbecause of his age, threw a glass
OL,15,Fbottle at police officers and was part
OL,16,Fof a mob who surrounded one police
OL,17,Fofficer who had his hat stolen.
