OL,3,CJail warning for teen who threw bottle
OL,4,Cand stole policeman's hat during riots
OL,6,FDistrict Judge, Jane Hamilton, told
OL,7,Fthe youngster, who has no previous
OL,8,Fconvictions, that the court only had
OL,9,Fthe power to impose two sentences,
OL,10,Feither a referral order or time in
OL,11,Fcustody.
OL,13,FJudge Hamilton adjourned sentencing to
OL,14,F1 October, for the preparation of a
OL,15,Fpre-sentence report.
OL,17,FShe bailed the boy, warning him:
OL,18,F"Obviously this was a large-scale
OL,19,Fdisturbance, that means the court must
OL,20,Flook at whether you should go to
OL,21,Fcustody.
